data.description: This beautifully recently remodeled  home is located in the highly desirable community of Sun City which offers access to a wealth of amenities for residents, including golf courses, community centers, fitness facilities and social clubs. This charming home has been tastefully updated with modern features! The bedrooms are generously sized and offer ample closet space and its spacious living area offers plenty of natural light- perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. Additional features of the home include a large indoor laundry area and a low-maintenance yard, making this home the perfect lock-and-leave seasonal home or full time live in property. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a stunning home in Sun City Arizona!
